      "role": "user",
      "content": "less than 1%... that's basically saying it's impossible. so what you're saying is that for people like me, the science has essentially reached a dead end. if the medical community knows the odds are that bad, why does everyone keep pushing these useless treatments instead of just being honest that for a large portion of us, there's no way out?",
